    "Seunghoo and Juhun (2024) propose a new algorithm called \"Concept Eraser\".",
    "This method achieves the goal of removing or replacing specific concepts in the pre-trained model by modifying the drift of the classifier guide term and the unconditional score term.",
    "This algorithm can not only effectively erase the object concept, but also maintain the generative ability of the model.",
    "The proliferation of fake images, with their deceptive nature, has the potential to mislead the public, distort the truth, and contribute to misunderstanding and panic.",
    "It can harm trust, disrupt social stability, and have negative effects on individual reputation and mental health (Shen et al. 2019; Nash et al. 2009)."
